folder: Gun Hill Road (East) & Willett Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Willett Avenue
text:
E. Gunhill Road, north side, east from Willett Avenue to White Plains Road, showing the Williamsbridge station of the I.R.T. subway. The 3-story building, on the left, is at the N.E. corner of Willett Avenue.
May 12, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
